_json.gridTitle: Top 10 Aluminium Foil Uses You Didn't Know About
_json.description: Aluminium foil can be used for many other things except for the kitchen needs we all know about. Actually, this foil can be very useful when it comes to fixing and organizing little things in the house. There are many uses, starting with using the foil to prevent bananas from getting brown too quickly, or using it to sharpen your scissors.
